            <li>Maps must be made in the osu! standard game mode.</li>
            <li>
                You may participate alone or as a team of 2 people, in which
                case the prize will be split.
            </li>
            <li>
                You may not submit a map that has been uploaded to the osu!
                website before the start of the event.
            </li>
            <li>
                Your map should be submitted with a short text, explaining some
                of the ideas that you used for your map, to help us better
                understand creative decisions when grading.
            </li>
            <li>
                All content in the map must adhere to this server's rules (e.g.
